'''Harov''' (also Garov, {{lang-hy|Հարավ - '''Harav'''}}) is a village in the [[Khojali Rayon]] of [[Azerbaijan]]. Since the [[Nagorno-Karabakh war]] the town has been administered by the ''de facto'' [[Nagorno-Karabakh Republic]] as part of [[Askeran Region|Askeran Province]].<ref>http://census.stat-nkr.am/nkr/1-1.pdf</ref>


