ocrite || Meyrin || Meyrin, Prévessin-Moëns ||data-sort-value="Democritus"|[[Democritus]] (c.460 BC-c.370 BC) |- |Route Dirac || Prévessin || Prévessin-Moëns, Saint-Genis-Pouilly ||data-sort-value="Dirac, Paul"|[[Paul Dirac]] (1902-1984) |- |Route Einstein || Meyrin || Meyrin, Prévessin-Moën ||data-sort-value="Einstein, Albert"|[[Albert Einstein]] (1879-1955) |- |Route Faraday || Meyrin || Meyrin, Satigny || [[Michael Faraday]] |- |Route Fermi || Meyrin || Saint-Genis-Pouilly || [[Enrico Fermi]] |- |Route Feynman || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Richard Feynman]] |- |Square Galileo Galilei || LHC Point 1 || Meyrin ||data-sort-value="Galilei, Galileo"|[[Galileo Galilei]] (1564-1642) |- |Route Gauss || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Carl Friedrich Gauss]] |- |Route Gentner || Prévessin || Prévessin-Moëns, Saint-Genis-Pouilly || [[Wolfgang Gentner]] |- |Route Goward || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Frank Kenneth Goward]] |- |Route Gregory || Meyrin || Prévessin-Moëns, Saint-Genis-Pouilly || [[Bernard Gregory]] |- |Route Greinacher || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Heinrich Greinacher]] |- |Route H. Cavendish || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Henry Cavendish]] |- |Route Heisenberg || Prévessin || Prévessin-Moëns || [[Werner Heisenberg]] |- |Route Hertz || Meyrin || Meyrin ||data-sort-value="Hertz, Heinrich"|[[Heinrich Hertz]] (1857-1894) |- |Route Joliot-Curie || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Frédéric Joliot-Curie]] |- |Route J. Perrin || Meyrin || Saint-Genis-Pouilly || [[Jean Baptiste Perrin]] |- |Square Lagarrigue || Meyrin || Satigny ||data-sort-value="Lagarrigue, André"|[[André Lagarrigue]] (1924-1975) |- |Route Lagarrigue || Prévessin || Prévessin-Moëns ||data-sort-value="Lagarrigue, André"|[[André Lagarrigue]] (1924-1975) |- |Route Lawrence || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Ernest Lawrence]] |- |Route Maxwell || Meyrin || Meyrin, Satigny || [[James Clerk Maxwell]] |- |Route Newton || Meyrin || Meyrin || [[Isaac Newton]] |- |Route Oppenheimer || Meyrin || Prévessin-Moëns, Saint-Genis-Pouilly || [[Robert Oppenheimer]] |- |R